               stealing a leather pocket-book, value 6 d. the property of the <rs id="t17800913-17-viclabel96" type="occupation">Rev</rs>
                     <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17800913-17-victim181 t17800913-17-viclabel96"></join>. 
