                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17800913-17-defend178 t17800913-17-punish100"></join>
               Navigation 2 years
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Tried by the First Middlesex Jury before Mr. Justice BULLER.</p>
